{"tid":1043942,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Map定高德","createTime":"2019-03-02T14:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T13:04:11.000Z","uid":165849,"like":46,"dislike":186,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"7564aadae06db67abb129c8cc592e945795c777c","tid":1043942,"uid":165849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"好似好多人用高德，但好似都有啲問題⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Google Map: 有時帶錯路，見塞車會帶你兜遠啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高德: 簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，地圖唔update，搵唔到中環灣仔繞道"},{"pid":"32680a5a37853b9d1167b11c4a9042007acedc54","tid":1043942,"uid":208241,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"waze"},{"pid":"75b245155c7739459cb82459f2bbad671b5a2f64","tid":1043942,"uid":31029,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"剩係高德個路線圖都贏十九幾條街<br />\nWAZE就語音導航正 同埋更新得快"},{"pid":"7932005bb1fc04c20ba1ad059c390dd087ffa38a","tid":1043942,"uid":41853,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾google搵唔撚到地鐵站岀入口"},{"pid":"d67dffb2267f3757f74817620f941f3077cf2929","tid":1043942,"uid":111872,"like":55,"dislike":3,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"以前都覺得用大陸app 好柒所以唔用<br />\n但好多frd 都叫我用高德<br />\n最近轉返黎用<br />\n真係好過google map 好多<br />\n唯一唔好就係講太多野聽唔到歌<br />\n但對於完全唔識路既話<br />\n佢講越多資料越好<br />\n講得好清晰而且會不停提醒你<br />\n去到路口位仲有放大路線圖<br />\n仲會提埋你依加行緊條路限速幾多<br />\n用落感覺真係差好遠<br />\n<br />\n用google map 去d未去過既地方<br />\n有一半機會會行錯<br />\n久唔久就冇啦啦叫你U Turn<br />\nd 上橋落橋位又唔清晰<br />\n成日帶帶下以為仲行岩條路<br />\n點知原來show 緊上/下面條路<br />\n越行越錯<br />\n<br />\nps: 高德有得轉繁體"},{"pid":"ee625d3880b000317889ec8715a1f3ba66140ef1","tid":1043942,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32680a5a37853b9d1167b11c4a9042007acedc54","tid":1043942,"uid":208241,"l